nodes.text: The Clone Wars: Decide Your Destiny: Tethan Battle Adventure
Tethan Battle Adventure is a "Decide Your Destiny" young-reader book published in July 2009. This book is based on the Star Wars: The Clone Wars film.
This is a gallery of different cover variations of The Clone Wars: Decide Your Destiny: Tethan Battle Adventure.
